| <!-- ADD CATEGORIES BELOW THIS LINE, PLEASE: -->
[[Category:Date mathematics templates]]
[[Category:Templates generating hAtom]]
[[Category:Templates generating hCalendars]]
[[Category:Templates generating hCards]]
}}</includeonly>

